flowchart LR
    AppServer1[App Server 1] --> HashRing[Consistent\nHash Ring]
    AppServer2[App Server 2] --> HashRing
    AppServer3[App Server 3] --> HashRing

    subgraph CacheCluster[Cache Cluster]
        HashRing --> CacheNode1[(Cache Node 1\nKeys: A-H)]
        HashRing --> CacheNode2[(Cache Node 2\nKeys: I-P)]
        HashRing --> CacheNode3[(Cache Node 3\nKeys: Q-Z)]
    end

    CacheNode1 --> CacheHit{Cache\nHit?}
    CacheHit -->|Yes| ReturnValue[Return cached\nvalue to app]
    CacheHit -->|No - Miss| QueryDB[Query Primary\nDatabase]
    QueryDB --> DB[(Primary Database)]
    DB --> WriteCache[Write result\nto cache node + TTL]
    WriteCache --> ReturnValue

    AppServer1 -->|Write / Update| InvalidateCache[Invalidate\ncache key]
    InvalidateCache --> CacheCluster
    AppServer1 -->|Write / Update| DB
